quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,96,"Uye dai vanhu vemumadhorobha vakatenda uye nekutya (Allah), zvirokwazvo, dai takavazarurira makomborero kubva kudenga uye nepanyika, asi vakaramba (vatumwa). Nokudaro takavaranga pamusana peizvo zvavaiwana (kusatenda nezvitadzo)"
  7,97,Saka vanhu vemumadhorobha vanonzwa kusununguka here kubva mukuuya kwemutongo wedu panguva dzemanheru apo pavanenge vakarara
  7,98,Kana kuti vanhu vemumadhorobha vanonzwa kusununguka here kubva mukuuya kwemutongo wedu panguva dzemasikati apo pavanenge vachitamba
  7,99,"Vanonzwa kusununguka here kubva muhurongwa hwaAllah? Hapana anonzwa kusununguka kubva muhurongwa hwaAllah, kusara kweavo vanhu vakarasikirwa"
  7,100,"Hazvina kujeka here kune avo vakagara nyika nhaka mushure mevanhu vayo (vaivapo ivo vasati vavapo), kuti dai taida, tingadai takavaparadza nokuda kwezvivi zvavo. Uye tikava tinovhara moyo yavo kuti vasave vanonzwa"
  7,101,"Ayo aiva madhorobha nyaya yavo tirikukuudza (Muhammad (SAW)). Uye zvirokwazvo, vatumwa vavo vakauya kwavari nehumboo uri pachena, asi havana kuve vanotenda mune zvavakaramba pakutanga. Saizvozvo, Allah vanovhara moyo yeavo vasingatendi"
  7,102,"Uye vazhinji vavo, hatina kuwana chokwadi muzvitsidzo zvavo, asi vazhinji vavo takavaona zvirokwazvo vari vatadzi"
  7,103,"Nokudaro, mushure mavo takatumira Musa nezviratidzo zvedu kuna Farawo nemadzishe ake, asi vakazviramba. Naizvozvo chionai kuti akange ari sei magumo evakonzeri venyonga-nyonga"
  7,104,"Uye Musa akati: “Iwe Farawo! Zvirokwazvo, ndiri mutumwa kubva kuna Tenzi vepasi rose.”"